{"tid":2008232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲飲starbucks？不了，飲Blue Bottle Coffee啦","createTime":"2020-05-09T01:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T02:48:06.000Z","uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"976f9b77671af8f57118f0713d562070331bcd2f","tid":2008232,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:46:49.000Z","msg":"2018年高調進軍香港市場的著名內地飲品店喜茶(HEYTEA)，原本在港有八間分店，當時被不少香港年輕人視為潮飲，事實上喜茶未攻港前，不少港人每逢周末過關為飲一杯喜茶。然而進駐香港後不足兩年，因疫情與反修例事件持續，現時只縮減至兩間，喜茶官方Facebook上只列出沙田新城市廣場及銅鑼灣時代廣場兩間分店。喜茶昔日門外永遠都是長長的人龍 ，惟記者昨天走訪沙田新城市廣場的分店，發現人龍不見；反而近日新進駐香港有「咖啡界Apple」之稱的Blue Bottle Coffee受港人熱捧，中環新開張即大排長龍，<strong>買一杯Cappuccino要排45分鐘</strong>。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n對於內地攻港的喜茶在香港分店連接倒閉，排緊隊光顧Blue Bottle的陳小姐說：「正常啦，過去依一年大家都知道發生咩事，香港人應該支持咩鋪頭，大家都心中有數！」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n以芝士奶蓋茶聞名的喜茶，由內地的「90後」聶雲宸於2012年創辦，在內地急速發展，成為內地新一代最潮的消費，分店遍佈全中國，新加坡亦有分店，當時更有不少港人逢周末過關為飲一杯喜茶。喜茶2018年高調進軍香港，更成為財經及文化界熱話，首間香港分店於沙田新城市廣場開幕時，一度吸引數百人打蛇餅排隊「朝聖」，人龍幾近企滿大半個樓層位置，要<strong>輪候超過四小時才成功購得飲品</strong>。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/29658/%E5%96%9C%E8%8C%B6-%E8%97%8D%E7%93%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1_blue_bottle_coffee-%E6%8E%92%E9%9A%8A-29658/%E5%96%9C%E8%8C%B68%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97%E8%AE%8A2%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%A9%E8%A6%8B-%E7%BE%8E%E8%B3%87blue-bottle%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%9245%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E8%B2%B7cappuccino\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F29658%2F%25E5%2596%259C%25E8%258C%25B6-%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%2593%25B6%25E5%2592%2596%25E5%2595%25A1_blue_bottle_coffee-%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%259A%258A-29658%2F%25E5%2596%259C%25E8%258C%25B68%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25BA%2597%25E8%25AE%258A2%25E9%2596%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B3%2587blue-bottle%25E5%2592%2596%25E5%2595%25A1%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%258E%259245%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E8%25B2%25B7cappuccino&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=64142a46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/29658/%E5%96%9C%E8%8C%B6-%E8%97%8D%E7%93%B6%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1_blue_bottle_coffee-%E6%8E%92%E9%9A%8A-29658/%E5%96%9C%E8%8C%B68%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97%E8%AE%8A2%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%A9%E8%A6%8B-%E7%BE%8E%E8%B3%87blue-bottle%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%9245%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E8%B2%B7cappuccino</a>"},{"pid":"0fbb0a5f2111985a2dcb7f91254312ea2d9e93e0","tid":2008232,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"喜茶8間分店變2間人龍不復見　美資Blue Bottle咖啡店排45分鐘買Cappuccino<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38947e13aad87538be5cd814871dee5b51bdb2f1","tid":2008232,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea0ff9e3c76f03710d374754a55ca69133bd75d","tid":2008232,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"咖啡撚 - Blue Bottle 算唔算藍店<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b6c3437f721b117f82a225a1458a31370cf88b","tid":2008232,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:39:04.000Z","msg":"不了 飲獨立黃店"},{"pid":"ca9e51559a81a041bed4f6104c097f0ecf8ef423","tid":2008232,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解飲杯咖啡要等咁耐，有咩過人之處？"},{"pid":"3104918bca47e5e817aac959d67dd234f426910c","tid":2008232,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:48:06.000Z","msg":"starbucks pacific依兩間難飲過屎水 不如慳返d錢買涼茶。"}]}